1. Hosting the game
   upload the game folder in c-panel and extract the folder
   then create a node.js app, select domain or subdomain and the game folder
   then run code npm install and then npm start
   the game will run on domain or subdomain
2. WordPress Integration
   create a page in wordpress for the game
   Insert iframe via Elementor HTML widget or shortcode.
   Ensure HTTPS is enabled for Firebase and game.
   then game will be available in wordpress.
   example code:
   // functions.php
   function embed_phaser_game() {
   $iframe = '<iframe 
           src="https://yourappname.com" 
           width="800" height="600" 
           style="border:none;overflow:hidden;" 
           allowfullscreen
           loading="lazy"></iframe>';
   return $iframe;
   }
   add_shortcode('phaser_game', 'embed_phaser_game');

for run in localhost:
extact the game folder and open terminal in the folder
run command
npm install
npm start
the game will be hosted on localhost:3002 port
